title: Arsenal accused of lack of respect after leaving non-league Sutton’s away changing room in a tip – and they even left milk on the radiator!
text:
EFL Room for improvement Arsenal accused of lack of respect after leaving non-league Sutton’s away changing room in a tip – and they even left milk on the radiator! 
Pictures emerged of the mess the Gunners left the facilities with a drinks littering the floor and a milk bottle left on a radiator By LEE ASTLEY
